OL,3,CHundreds stuck on cruise ship in
OL,4,CFrance after suspected norovirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FHundreds of people are being held on a
OL,8,Fcruise ship in France after a
OL,9,Fsuspected norovirus outbreak.
OL,11,FSeveral passengers on board the
OL,12,FAmbition have shown symptoms linked to
OL,13,Fthe virus, according to Ambassador
OL,14,FCruise Line, which owns the ship.
OL,16,FThe company said the ship is currently
OL,17,Fdocked in Bordeaux and has seen cases
OL,18,Frise since passengers boarded in
OL,19,FLiverpool on May 9.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
