OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778702756
OL,3,CHundreds stuck on cruise ship in
OL,4,CFrance after suspected norovirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FThe vessel was due to be on a 14-night
OL,8,Fwestern France and Spain explorer
OL,9,Fcruise.
OL,11,FIn a social media post on Wednesday,
OL,12,Fthe cruise ship's owner said:
OL,13,F"Ambassador Cruise Line can confirm
OL,14,Fthat a number of guests and crew
OL,15,Fonboard Ambition have displayed or are
OL,16,Fdisplaying symptoms consistent with
OL,17,Fgastrointestinal illness (GII) during
OL,18,Fthe 14-night Delights of Western
OL,19,FFrance & Spain Explorer sailing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
