OL,3,CHundreds stuck on cruise ship in
OL,4,CFrance after suspected norovirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,F"The GII illness is the most common
OL,8,Fcause of the 'winter vomiting bug' or
OL,9,F'stomach flu'.
OL,11,F"The ship departed Belfast on Friday 8
OL,12,FMay and Liverpool on Saturday 9 May
OL,13,F2026, with our figures reporting an
OL,14,Fincrease in cases following the
OL,15,Fembarkation of guests in Liverpool.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
