OL,3,CHundreds stuck on cruise ship in
OL,4,CFrance after suspected norovirus
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,F"We would like to reassure guests that
OL,8,Fwe take any illnesses onboard our
OL,9,Fships extremely seriously. Enhanced
OL,10,Fsanitation and prevention protocols
OL,11,Fwere immediately implemented across
OL,12,Fthe ship in line with established
OL,13,Fpublic health procedures following the
OL,14,Finitial reports of illness."
OL,16,FThis is a breaking story, more to
OL,17,Ffollow...
